REM windows_task_manager.duck
REM Opens Task Manager directly via Ctrl+Shift+Esc (bypasses the Ctrl+Alt+Del screen).
REM Ctrl+Alt+Del cannot be intercepted by HID devices — this is the correct approach.
REM Works on Windows 10 and 11.
REM Copy to: /sdcard/lab/ble/blueduck/scripts/

HUMAN_MODE OFF

CTRL-SHIFT ESC
